cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SD, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on multimodal machine learning for sentiment analysis, which involves processing language, visual, and acoustic modalities. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes two methods for unsupervised learning of joint multimodal representations using sequence to sequence (Seq2Seq) methods. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing visual modalities for sentiment analysis. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a possible category as the paper deals with processing acoustic modalities for sentiment analysis. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also be applicable as the paper deals with developing machine learning models for sentiment analysis.
